title: #7【FF9】完全初見でファイナルファンタジーⅨを始める！ FINAL FANTASY Ⅸ ぺこ！【ホロライブ/兎田ぺこら】※ネタバレ注意
name: Usada Pekora

entries.text: Since I kept quiet about it later...
But yesterday was Valentine's, you know? That sort of thing.
I thought, "Ah, I really should make something."
Like, "I can't even do a membership stream."
Right, I couldn't do a membership stream either, so...
I thought I'd make something simple for a Short.
I wanted to make some sweets and post a picture.
Hmm, maybe Pekora is just bad at baking and love?
All I did was melt chocolate and butter, add milk, eggs, pancake mix, mix it, put it in the rice cooker, and press "beep."
But when I thought it was done, the top layer was kinda raw...
But I made it in a rice cooker, so there's no way I messed up the measurements.
I followed the Shorts person's recipe.
So I thought maybe my rice cooker's capacity...
"No, surely it's not undercooked?" I thought.
So I put it on "Rapid Cook" one more time.
And it was still a little raw-looking.
Pekora is impatient, so I stopped the rapid cooking halfway through.
I went with the "If I chill it..."
"...so that's why it looks raw," I told myself.
But since I'm impatient, I just took it out.
I was also getting kinda hungry.
I rushed to the supermarket to get a choco-pen.
I wrote with the choco-pen, snapped a picture...
And, well... maybe because of that...
Maybe it really was raw, I don't know, but...
My stomach felt a little off last night.
Like, "This is a weird stomach pain."
I figured everyone would think, "I'm only getting this from Pekora," so...
I thought I'd make something for you guys.
I didn't exactly get diarrhea, but...
It hurt. Like, "What is this pain?"
Or rather than quitting, I just didn't eat it yesterday.
Playing FF while eating nothing but yogurt...
I just got in the mood to eat rice instead of soba.
Also, for Valentine's, yes, "Love no Kasabuta" is out!
It was mixed by Nui Sociere-san.
Please listen to it a lot if you'd like.
Ah, let me talk a bit until Pekora finishes eating this yogurt.
This announcement was so last minute...
It's not Pekora's usual haughty vibe, but a bit more "sickly"...
Like a "Yami-Peko" (Dark Pekora). That kind of Pekora.
FF9, let's have fun today too!
I might be addicted to putting honey in my cereal.
Well, I only started doing it yesterday though.
Can I just put in my mouthpiece?
If I don't wear the mouthpiece...
I can do them without a mirror now.
Eh, you think so? Don't say that.
You move them to a nice position, right?
But if you stop using the mouthpiece...
"I want to go back to how I was before!"
Apparently, they go back little by little.
Actually, even after the straightening is done...
You have to use a retainer...
Apparently, you have to do it again basically.
How long do I have to do this?!
How long does teeth straightening take?
Seriously, everyone, take care of your teeth.
Buying some armor is a good idea.
Petan and the others have it, but...
I can't unequip them right now since they're over there.
Armor... is our defense bad here?
A magic party should be strong, surely!
For someone who isn't a mage...
I want something other than Healing Rod for Hime-san.
Ugh, should I buy this Green Beret?
Should I let them learn it?
I'll buy one Green Beret just in case.
Whatever, someone will use it. I'll buy one.
"Light the flame and the path shall open."
Means I have to light a fire?
"Sunlight Tree is the candy of power"?
"Hold up your hand and the brightness will not fade."
"The time of sunlight is the source of power."
It said something like "Light it up."
Oi, this guy isn't petrifying me, right?
Will I die if I summon twice?
Does it mean I can't summon?!
Oi, why can't I bring out Ifrit?!
Oi, getting hit with too much poison!
This is bad, I need to heal Dagger's heart quickly.
It's annoying for Eiko to do that.
Having no MP is kinda bad.
Ah, do I have Level 4 Holy?
Eh, well, surprisingly I haven't used many Tents.
I want her to get better, but...
Making her think "I hope you get better soon" might make it worse for her.
It might make her heart go "Ugh."
I want her to go at her own pace, but...
My eyes look weird. My eyes look weird.
"Light the path and it won't open."
Wait, I want to use this guy one more time...
Come on, if I can go...
Is that meant to weaken me more?!
It's messed up! Oi, stop joking! No miss! Oi Dagger is there!
Oh thanks, thanks for the healing.
Dagger, huh... Even if she's confused, it doesn't really hurt.
Not good... Did we have anything?
Whoa, there's a door over here.
What's this offering? "Extract from the armor granted with power."
Will you examine the light? Yes.
"If you skip all the fun, the path will open."
But, let's go to that place from before too.
The one with weak stats right now...
Since it's a King, an accessory...
I think I picked up something like armor.
That I take things like Fire and Thunder...
Or does it mean it makes them null?
Anyway, I can only use Repili.
Even if I could use it...
I'll attach Counter just in case.
Should I take the bottom one?
It's here so I just did it.
Gross, "Let's all sleep together," is it that kind of vibe?
Kino-san and the path is head-head-two... Yes, yes, yes.
Isn't this suspicious? Not suspicious here? I'll hit this too.
Oh, Kawaguchi... detour? This detour is a detour?
Twice is that... Magic evasion is zero... oh, there's something deep inside the thief place.
"An armlet once worn by a ninja."
If I can learn it, that's fine, but...
Well, let's make Vivi learn Water for now.
But where do I go from here?
Going back looks possible, doesn't it?
But it didn't light up just now.
I heard a Moogle sound though.
Doesn't seem like there are items here.
But it's weird that there's nothing after this.
"Do not chase the shadow of the wicked."
"Chase the shadow of the holy one."
Wait a sec, Hime-san has to learn it.
What was it? What did they give us?
Ah, Night's Heart is fine too.
Don't know what that means though.
I want a nice enemy ability.
What's annoying if they do it?
It's annoying if physical attacks miss.
Lowering physical accuracy is god-tier. Spending this much...
Don't know? Only goes up by 200?
Top tier. Freya-san is... MP is pretty...
All big costs. Is this it?
Magic Return is different now... feels like "It's not that good".
Did I come out in a different place?
I am in the next room.
I'm happy to meet you again.
Not giving me the time of day, huh.
I'm just having them sleep a little.
If by chance something happened to the Princess...
What should I do with myself?!
This bastard, how cowardly can you be?
Come on, will you hand it over or not?
This is a bit outside my calculations.
That's right, the ones inside here are fakes.
But that doesn't mean the game is decided.
How will this Cid do... this frog?
Are you okay? Cid hasn't been squashed?
But I guess it's no good.
After I killed Cid and took the Gulug Stone from you...
I intended to dispose of you all too, but...
For now, I'll take her and this.
There's something about it, this Summon.
Hope we can meet again someday.
He plans to escape on the Hilda Garde I.
Here, I want all three of these.
I'll steal, so until then, firepower...
Have to raise her as a healer.
Man, I want to bring Vivi but...
I don't think she'll stop though.
Right now her heart is wounded.
She's definitely not in good shape, but...
I feel like, "Can I really abandon a girl like that?"
I guess I'll protect her in the back.
Anyway, let's protect the girls with Phoenix.
Looks like we have no choice but to chase.
I want to check the room, is there one?
There are 6 people so whatever, stop it.
Cards are enough treasure, cards are enough.
If we chase with the Blue Narciss...
I intended to do that without you telling me.
Does he intend to extract them?
How do we go on this?
But now it's Eiko rather than Dagger.
So it's Eiko over Dagger now.
Fast! Eh, eh, the ship is fast!
Isn't the Hilda Garde I surprisingly slow?
What on earth is beyond that?
I don't even want to understand what he's thinking, but...
That little girl uses summons, right?
Like when he stole from Dagger again...
I won't let him have his way.
Oi, if Phoenix gets extracted, that's painful.
Also, we need to catch him...
I did the Idest Daiji too.
This place is nice. Look, Choco-choco.
Sorry Choco, I know it's cold.
Right, basically Quina is top priority.
Starting with Quina's appetite isn't good.
Stop it, I'm getting killed in a res-kill state.
Did you see someone who looks just like Vivi?
I am the Bishop of this holy land, Est Gaza.
Are you companions of that noisy group?
Was there a girl among them?
Our friend's life is at stake.
If you know, please tell us.
And all life returns to the Planet.
Passing through the path of souls.
Wasn't there a girl with the Black Mages?
And everyone from the Black Mage Village came too, right?
They pushed in with great numbers.
That must be the Black Mage army.
They proceeded towards Mount Gulug ahead.
This mountain is called Mount Gulug.
Will it erupt then? Even though it looks so cold?
There are rumors that creatures called Moles used to live inside the volcano long ago.
But that is a very old story.
Ever since someone sealed the entrance...
It's a place no one visits.
Their objective appears to be Mount Gulug.
So the girl was with them too.
Come to think of it, a Black Mage was carrying a girl.
If we know that, we can't dawdle!
We're going to Mount Gulug too!
Is there a shop line here?
A place to sort out equipment...
The Shimmering Island can only be seen from here.
Rumor has it the Bishop sometimes hears voices from the path of souls.
Should I buy a Heavy Lance?
Should I buy it for them?
Won't it fill up after 2 or 3 battles?
Ah, I can go this way.
Ah, I can throw this too.
I stopped here to see you.
Well, I'm happy even if it's flattery.
I'm Lisa. I meet Guts here sometimes.
Let's go see the Shimmering Island together.
You'll get kicked by a horse one of these days.
There's a noisy one, so next time then.
The glow of the Shimmering Island is proof that place is the path of souls.
Is that it? No one else?
Are there Moogles, Molicia or Mogne?
It's kind of scary so I want you to read it with me, kupo.
I said it was no good.
Doesn't it look like a house?
Then let's go that way first.
Told to go to the volcano but...
I thought this proceeds the story so I did it, but...
Does it mean "I want to go there"?
Wait a sec, this is bad!
It was okay, but not really...
Get this guy, first get one!
Petan will die from Vacuum Wave.
What is up with this guy, seriously?
I must obtain an Eidolon with power greater than Alexander.
An Eidolon with power enough to bury Terra.
As I am now, I'll be easily erased.
I must defeat him before Terra's plan activates...
Or I will cease to be me.
Who cares about a little girl's nonsense?
Be it the desire to live...
Or the desire to protect others...
Even if it is another's soul...
If there is a soul with massive power surpassing all...
I have no more use for you.
These twins are sufficient opponents for you.
They were getting beaten up earlier though.
Weren't the people of my village twins?
If you don't go, you'll be changed, right?
What happened to the other Black Mages?
Well, she's dressed very nicely so...
No, why are you here too?
Eh, what is this? What does it mean?
Eh, what exactly does that mean?
He was a polite man towards women.
But that man seems to talk a bit too much.
Hmm, what do you mean, kero?
Even though I didn't ask questions...
He would unilaterally talk about his goals and such.
But the content of that talk was terrifying.
He is a human from a world different from this one...
And intends to use this world to gain massive power.
Ah, someone from another world is coming.
It was there yesterday too, fusing Earth and something...
Probably the other one's guy, surely.
It seems he stole the Hilda Garde I at all costs.
We need to tell Petan and the others later.
Anyway, kidnapping me didn't seem to be the goal.
From his way of speaking about himself, I felt he was quite a narcissist...
At least he doesn't seem to be a philanderer like you.
I'm already reflecting on that matter.
That's why I braved danger to go help you.
Didn't you just want to take back the Hilda Garde I?
So turn me back into a human quickly, kero!
I'm sick of being a frog or a bug, kero!
I absolutely won't cheat again, kero! Forgive me, kero!
I won't lie! I have only you, kero!
Understood. I shall turn you back.
But the next time you try to cheat, it won't end with a bug.
I understand, kero! Make me a Hedgehog Pie next time maybe!
Spare me just that, kero! Anyway, hurry up, kero!
Now we can start construction on the No. 3 in earnest, buri!
No good, haven't shaken old habits.
Lady Hilda is calling, so please come to the conference room.
Wanted to watch a bit longer though.
No, nothing, don't worry about it.
Do you get woken up during good dreams?
Was it about to get steamy?
But if you sleep too much...
Seriously, I feel like you have nightmares.
When I sleep too much, I wake up from a nightmare.
Will you tell us the whole plan?
Eh, conference room is this way.
No really, try sleeping to death.
In a death game is high.
Geez, still haven't shook the frog speech.
I didn't call everyone to talk about that.
I gathered you to convey what I heard...
While I was imprisoned by Kuja.
It might be a clue to his whereabouts.
I shall go look for her immediately!
I will start construction of the No. 3 at once.
We will likely use the Blue Narciss.
What kind of story is it?
It is hard to believe instantly, but...
Kuja intends to use this world...
What's he gonna do with that?
Also, Kuja seems not to be a human of this world.
The world we live in is called Gaia, but...
Kuja called the world he was born in "Terra."
Have to fix it little by little.
Even if we work and work...
Only high places, wish someone would swap with me.
Steiner came all the way here?
What are you all gathering for?
Old man, that's not a nice way to say it.
We were consulting on restoring the Theater District, zura.
With that worried look on your face, can't be nothing.
She wasn't found in the castle...
So I thought she might have come to town.
Rather than you searching, unaccustomed to this town...
It's faster and surer if we search.
Tantalus people are seriously nice guys.
Terra and this world seem connected by a place called Shimmering Island.
I don't know where Kuja ran, but...
If we go there, we might manage something.
However, it seems you cannot go directly to Terra from the Shimmering Island.
That's right, the world isn't that sweet.
If so, everyone would know about that other world by now. True.
There is more to this story.
The place connecting the two worlds is apparently sealed...
But he said there is a place that serves as a key to unlock the seal.
Kuja said it's an old castle north of the Forgotten Continent.
The old castle on the Forgotten Continent remains in the records of the adventurer Ipsen.
According to that, exploration was abandoned due to deep cliffs.
Either way, the Forgotten Continent itself isn't well known, so I can't say much.
For now, since it has no name, let's call it Ipsen's Castle.
Well, places other than this continent aren't well known.
Kuja talks a lot, doesn't he?
You finally returned to human form!
Now we can start construction properly!
For construction, using the lessons from No. 2...
The engine parts are mostly complete.
This is proving more difficult than expected.
About the hull, I intend to reuse the Blue Narciss.
The hull itself is very well made.
Well, that's not the only reason.
We have circumstances requiring hasty completion.
The blueprints are complete in my head.
If you follow my instructions, it won't be difficult.
Isn't it playing right into Kuja's hand?
It's because we're dancing in his palm...
Well, maybe it's like "I'll let you live and talk so you'll make this move."
Yeah, purposefully letting her speak and stay alive to make us come.
Or maybe, like she said, he's soft on women.
But he tried to kill Eiko.
If we go to Ipsen's Castle, we might learn something.
Did you get that out of the villain?
I never "got it out of him."
While talking, he got drunk on his own words...
He spoke of this and that.
Besides, even if he told me...
He probably thought it irrelevant to his goal.
True, if we fought him properly...
Power like ours wouldn't even reach his feet.
But I can absolutely never forgive Kuja.
The problem is how to get there.
Since Blue Narciss is used for No. 3...
Do we have to wait for No. 3's completion?
Eh, wait, she's not in Lindblum either?
Well, yeah. Where did she go?
I'll bring her back right away.
Didn't have it from the start but...
I'll ask customers coming to my place.
If anything comes up, I'll contact you.
Seriously, Tantalus guys are too nice.
I was sure she came to Alexandria.
I felt like "that person" was here.
"Still, Miss, you survived? You are Baku..."
"Wow, the very Baku who kidnapped the Princess from the sister's place? Please don't worry about that, it's distant past."
"If you say so, I'll gratefully accept those words. Not that I care much though."
Boss, by "that person", you meant Beatrix?
As you can see, Alexandria was completely destroyed.
I tried to protect Alexandria with Steiner amidst the chaos, but...
Also, Dagger stopped speaking from the shock.
Lady Garnet shouldn't return to this city for a while.
Returning here would only deepen the wounds in her heart.
We thought she returned to this city...
Lady Garnet would definitely stop by that place.
Please tell her not to worry about Alexandria.
Tell her to cherish her own heart and body right now.
And one thing I want you to give her.
May that become Lady Garnet's strength.
I... I've been thinking ever since then.
I have to become Queen and restore peace to Alexandria.
But can I stay with Petan and the others a little longer?
Why? Can I ask the reason?
I only thought of things like that.
When I tried to become Queen, it was the same.
But no matter how hard I try now...
Surely the people won't accept me as Queen.
I have no right to protect this country.
That gem, see... initially it was just a stone found anywhere.
Using that wish as a clue...
The stone passed from person to person...
And now it shines in Dagger's hand.
If Dagger possesses the courage to shine...
Surely you will shine one day.
The time when Alexandria needs you will definitely come.
What's important is wishing to shine.
Saying I want to stay together with half-hearted feelings.
Even if the words are half-hearted...
If the feeling of wanting to be together is real, it's fine.
I want you to lend me *that* again.
What made me make a big decision back then.
Even though it takes considerable resolve.
No need for Pekora to cut it.
No one cuts their hair just because someone said something mean!
Oi, don't misunderstand on your own...
Does short hair not suit me?
N-Not at all! It suits you very well!
Wait, is this Erin the Erin-kun who lost to me in cards?
Right, we head there to solve the mystery of Shimmering Island, the entrance to Terra.
Surely if we reach Terra, we'll understand everything.
Yes, what Kuja is doing, and why he is doing this.
Ipsen's Castle is marked on the map based on Lady Hilda's info.
Please check with Minus 2 after departure.
Also if you align with the dot on the map and press A, auto-pilot... eh?
The system will work ahead, so please try it.
If you wish to change members...
It feels weird not to include her.
Right? She looks meta... or rather...
No, but the level gap is terrible, too much.
Oh, it does it automatically here.
But I want to do the girls...
I want to level them up but...
Should I do it at Mount Gulug?
If I level at Mount Gulug...
Anyway, check one of these first.
"I see something like a river, kupo."
I had to look for footprints.
Thinking about it, Dagger and others...
I want to give Hermes Shoes.
I kinda want to give Hermes Shoes, but...
Healing Rod should be changeable too.
Girls, sorry I haven't been taking care of you properly.
Making Hime-san wear a Judo uniform...
I want to equip them with something good.
I've been letting the guys wear all the good stuff, probably.
Even though my spirit is to be kind to girls.
I want to cast Haste on them.
Near a city where wind blows.
The place where Cleyra got beaten up.
My memory of how terrifying summons are faded for a moment.
Even though I learned the terror of FF9 summons. The movie was strongest.
I love Chocobos so much I'm dreaming?
Suddenly something appeared, what is this?
You seek a peaceful life with Chocobos.
Eh, why is the red one sparkling?
Gained the ability to go over shallow ocean.
You can reach the shallows via sandy beaches.
Still a long way to go, but you took a great step.
Eh, is this the story of becoming Fat Chocobo?
Is this the story of becoming Fat Chocobo?
There are too many small islands around...
I heard a rumor that there are shallows somewhere, kupo.
Might be related to that, kupo?
Small island beach is perfect for a resort, kupo.
This means I can get it now.
First time seeing this Chocobo evolution thing maybe.
This is the small island on the continent.
The place on Mist Continent with lots of small islands.
Found it, found it, found it.
Gonna need tons of greens, huh.
Oi Choco, aren't you rapidly evolving?
This white thing isn't there though.
Huh? I feel like it's not this.
There are small islands on this side too, surely.
Small island beach, perfect for a resort.
Not this. Looks like a small island but...
Shape-wise... no wait, this? No, too square.
It's weirdly shallow here. Or maybe here too... there's one here.
Pretty much everywhere is long here.
Come here Choco, I'll call you again.
There's an extension to the right.
Wait, I can't see the forest.
But here... is this like a small island?
Ah, looks like I can go there.
How far can I go like this?
I really feel like it does though.
If there are no Chocobo footprints...
If it's even a little far, will I get hunted by monsters again?
If it's up to here... hey.
Making me take quite a detour.
The ocean floor is harder than the forest...
I don't need greens at this depth.
Isn't it better to do it in the forest?
Isn't it better to do it in the forest?
And, I can't go to the Legendary Paradise anyway, right? Huh?
Tell me it's not there, then I'll give up.
I learned how kind the forest was.
Eh, where? If I get one, does it disappear?
But well, maybe because it's small, it's easier to get?
Crap, hitting a swamp ends it.
Well well well, money is fine.
I'm moving by the millimeter here.
Looking at it like "Consider this kind of place and it's easier"...
Feel like it got easier to dig.
Pekora was looking at the beak the whole time.
True if I verify from Petan's position...
It puts out pieces, so no meaning right?
I can't leave this Digging Squad.
Want to become a Chocobo, really.
Lowell is doing it with her, right?
Let me do it for free!
Since I'm doing it this much.
I feel like it finally stopped giving Chocographs.
There is a city nearby where night never ends, kupo.
Did that come out already? Not yet?
It hasn't come out for a long time.
For a change of pace, I'll go once.
I won't be on the exploited side.
If it's not there, I'll leave okay?
Let's go, let's go, let's go.
Choco, sorry for leaving you in such a dangerous place. Forgive me.
Umm, where did I put Treno?
Well, the cat outside is crying, so it's fine.
As long as there are Chocobo footprints...
Called you to such a ridiculously far place.
You gained the ability to climb steep mountains.
A nostalgic darkness will guide you to home.
Because I don't need the forest anymore.
This means here is a river, right?
Huh? There was a weapon shop, right?
Pekora gets quite a lot of items, right?
I find trash treasures, don't I?
With 4 people, can we do it?
Ah wait, only one person? In the end?
But it seemed to have horns.
Ah, put on this Confusion Sword.
Eh, if I have Auto-Life, is Haste okay?
But seriously, enemies got stronger at Mount Gulug.
Is it bad if I don't raise the girls' levels, or levels in general?
First, test my skills here to see.
Since I'm a man, I have to protect the girls.
Will it fly? Doesn't look like it flies.
Was Bird Killer okay for this?
If it's 55, can do it immediately?
But the day it becomes useful will come.
How much money did I have?
What effect does Promist Ring have?
Gonna be yahoo when I sell.
I want you to do that.
The sensor is doing something crazy.
Probably ran out of money on the last one...
Any place I haven't been? Wait a sec.
Could it be he's doing it today too?
Should I go to Alexandria to see Kabao?
And take Steiner to see Beatrix?
Want to search for Kabao too.
Long time no see. I hope you are well.
Could I go from here with that bug?
Eh? I'll go to Alexandria a bit.
He got fast legs to run away.
"Felt like I became happy," that sucks.
Eh, did this only make me feel happy? Could it be?
That's not it, digging up junk.
I could do Chocographs 3 or 4 times if it were real.
Was it talking about this? The people saying fountain, fountain?
Thinking "What is it, what is it?"
Probably that, well, can do it in Alexandria too?
Ah, said go to forest too.
Already strong here like I'm invincible.
What's Dead Pepper? Something weird came out.
Like, there are no Chocographs here.
See, aren't there no graphs here anymore?
Oi, aren't there no Chocographs here, Mene?
Prized long ago as a spice.
But due to mist, can't harvest anymore, they said...
It might be useful for something...
A spice, huh. Don't cook though.
Well, if he says it'll be useful...
Since no graphs coming out now.
Like I'm in a demon realm.
Don't understand the deliciousness of this forest anymore.
Bro was beaten and hasn't returned for a while.
If I hadn't rushed Meshiamada card, Iria's clothes might have been finished.
Just moved from Lindblum which was attacked recently.
Came for honeymoon but the city ended up like this.
Can hammer nails with this frying pan.
If we try hard, we should restore it soon.
Having too much is also questionable.
If I let Kabao into the theater...
Person who wanted to be a Moogle and played lead in 2...
Did he only say "Kuppo" because he was a Moogle?
If he wanted to be a Moogle...
This kid is cute but personality is...
Have to give it to Modon?
There was something about jump rope.
Water got completely dirty, fish swimming...
Feeding water to fish and splash-splash...
Meow-meow guide book, someone tell me.
The guy I sought isn't here either.
Want to start by making a kitchen.
Since Pluto Knights evacuation guidance was good...
Castle town damage wasn't as bad as thought.
Eh, can't meet Beatrix or Kabao?
From today for how many days?
Hey Kabao, are you really the Kabao from back then?
A room should open by evening today.
If you can wait until then...
We can prepare a room, how is that?
Eh wait Kabao, what does this mean?
Oi Kabao, let me play the game.
Rather showing true colors with cards.
Wow Kabao, good, feels like my feelings cleared up.
Remained in my heart forever. Is Kabao alive? Is Kabao okay?
There was a story like that. What was it?
